The People of the State of Illinois ex rel. Stanley Barski, appellee, v. William E. Dever, mayor, et al., appellants.Gen. No. 30,400.

Thomson, P. J., dissenting.

Opinion filed March 10, 1926.Francis X. Busch, Corporation Counsel, for appellants; W. Arnold Amberg, Roy S. Gaskill and Michael L. Rosinia, Assistant Corporation Counsel, of counsel. No appearance for appellee. Mr. Justice O’Connor

delivered the opinion of the court.
